string.text:
Anti-pain remedy (nest No. 1, unpainted case. Used for fractures, extensive wounds and burns. One tablet per dose);
A remedy for poisoning with hazardous chemical substances (nest No. 2, yellow-green case. Take 1 capsule 20-30 minutes before entering a smoke (gassed) area, with a high risk of inhalation of CO - carbon monoxide, in a burning forest, during fire extinguishing operations and rescue of victims);
A remedy for organophosphorus poisoning (nest No. 3, syringe-tube with a red cap. For intramuscular use. Taken upon a Civil Defense signal);
Radioprotective agent No. 1 (nest No. 4, crimson-colored case. The contents of the case are taken 15-20 minutes before the expected irradiation);
Radioprotective agent No. 2 (nest No. 5, white case. Adults and children take 1 tablet before the expected irradiation or within 30 minutes after irradiation. Then 1 tablet daily after radioactive fallout. Children under 2 years old take 1/3 of a tablet);
Antibacterial agent No. 1 (nest No. 6, unpainted case. Taken in case of threat or bacterial infection, as well as in case of wounds and burns, the contents of the case, washed down with water. For children under 8 years of age, prohibited, from 8 to 12 years - 1 capsule per dose);
Antibacterial agent No. 2 (nest No. 7, unpainted case. Taken after irradiation in case of gastrointestinal disorders, 1 tablet 2 times a day. Not recommended for children);
Antiemetic (nest No. 9, blue case. Take 1 tablet immediately after irradiation. Children over 6 years old take 1/2 tablet);
Reserve antidote for organophosphorus compounds (antioxidant, socket No. 8, red case. The contents of the case are taken upon the Civil Defense signal. Children aged 5-12 years take 1 tablet).

Octinisept. Indications: treatment of skin and mucous membranes before diagnostic and surgical procedures in pediatric, surgical and obstetric-gynecological practice, in traumatology, proctology, dermatovenereology, otolaryngology, dentistry;
treatment of wound and burn surfaces; prevention of foot mycoses and interdigital mycoses.
In special cases it is recommended for hypertension and semi-fainting conditions.
